==English==
===Alternative forms===
* [[e-ddress]], [[e-dress]]

===Etymology===
Blend of '''[[e-]]''' ‘electronic’ + '''[[address]]'''.

===Noun===
'''eddress'''
# {{rfv-sense}} An [[email]] [[address]].

